tip.text: If you want to escape this cruel busy world, this is a good place to stay in Oslob, Cebu! I already want to come back!
Boodle fight style! Pinoy food at its best, served hot over banana leaves as plates.
Too expensive for its taste and serving size. But I gotta admit I fell in-love with their bathroom
When stressed, it's the comfort food zone! Love their HOUSE SPECIAL SET which gives you the  best of all worlds - Tacos, spaghetti and fried chicken 😍
Love their interior and their coffee. Simple coffee nook for people who wants something diff from your Usuals -- Starbucks
Strong drinks for strong hearts. Not for the WEAK. Beergharita and Sour Puss made my night!
Tell them to take out the cilantro if you hate it like I do 🙅🏼
Crazy about their Flat White! Love their magazine rack too! Here's to Darling magazine, the art of being a woman!

Traditional Korean Houses (Hanok) which will inspire your architectural palate and little cute shops which inspire touches of art in our daily lives 💙
Authentic Korean BBQ grilled by fire and drank with soju bombs will remain in my memories forever. Not to mention, cute corner cafes and superb interior designs made my Seoul adventure life-changing!
Iced Latte & Spicy Rigatoni just go well with any stress-related convos!
